    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Geelus vurkdraad gen.n. & sp.n., male and female genitalia, line drawings. A. Aedeagus, apex, laterally; B. Aedeagus, apex, dorsally; C. Aedeagus, laterally; D. Connective; E. Style; F. Genital capsule, laterally; G. Subgenital plate; H. Genital capsule, dorsally; I. Sternite 7; J. Sternite 7; K. Valvifer 1, laterally." ;
